Cinegear Site Map

Home (/#home)
 ├─ Hero Section
 │   ├─ Event headline (Cinegear World – Sandton Convention Centre)
 │   ├─ Date & Location
 │   ├─ Tagline / Value prop
 │   ├─ Primary CTA: Register Now → opens Register Modal
 │   └─ Secondary CTA: Apply to Exhibit → opens Exhibit Modal
 │
 └─ Navigation (sticky header)
     ├─ Home (#home)
     ├─ About (#about)
     ├─ Trends & Events (#trends)
     └─ CTAs (Register / Exhibit)

About (/#about)
 ├─ What / When / Where
 ├─ Who Should Attend
 ├─ Exhibitor Benefits
 └─ FAQs (expand/collapse)

Trends & Events (/#trends)
 ├─ 2025 Trends (card grid: Virtual Production, AI Pipeline, On-set Cloud, etc.)
 ├─ Highlighted Agenda / Schedule Teasers
 └─ CTA: “Get My Expo Pass” → Register Modal

CTAs (modal overlays, not separate pages)
 ├─ Register Modal
 │   ├─ Form (Name, Email, opt-in for updates)
 │   ├─ Privacy note
 │   └─ Success screen
 │
 └─ Exhibit Modal
     ├─ Form (Company, Contact, Email, Package tier)
     ├─ Info on exhibitor benefits
     └─ Success screen